                    has been authenticated to an Open Id Provider.
                </summary>

                <remarks>
                    Authentication is performed to an Open Id Provider through
                    Shell which passes it to platform for verification 
                    against a HealthVault account.
                </remarks>
            </documentation>
        </annotation>
